<h2>What do you do?</h2>
<p>
I use technological know-how to leverage my altruistic impact in the world -- or I will, soon enough. Any tips?
</p>

<h2>Why?</h2>
<p>
I code because I love it. I want to help bring justice to the world because it seems like one of the very few praiseworthy missions in life.
</p>

<h2>Recent thought or epiphany?</h2>
<p>
It is self-discipline, above all things, that causes pleasure.
</p>

